  <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary">
  <meta name="twitter:title" content="Free Income Tax Calculator 2025 | MyTaxCalcs">
  <meta name="twitter:description" content="Estimate your 2025 federal income tax, taxable income, refund, effective rate, and marginal rate.">
  <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" sizes="any">
  <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.svg" type="image/svg+xml">
  <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="/favicon.png">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <script async src="https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=G-FS9HCDT0D7"></script>
  <script>window.dataLayer=window.dataLayer||[];function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}gtag('js',new Date());gtag('config','G-FS9HCDT0D7');</script>
  <script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-5193834725888549" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  <style>
    .breadcrumb{max-width:780px;margin:0 auto;padding:14px 24px 0;font-size:.8rem;color:#6b7280;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;flex-wrap:wrap}
    .breadcrumb a{color:#16a34a;text-decoration:none}.breadcrumb a:hover{text-decoration:underline}
    .breadcrumb-sep{color:#d1d5db;font-size:.75rem}
    .calc-page{max-width:780px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px 60px}
    .calc-page-header{padding:28px 0 24px}
    .page-eyebrow{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;font-size:.75rem;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.08em;color:#16a34a;background:#ecfdf5;border-radius:20px;padding:4px 12px;margin-bottom:12px}
    .calc-page-header h1{font-size:2rem;font-weight:800;line-height:1.2;margin:0 0 10px;color:#111827}
    .calc-page-header p{font-size:1rem;color:#6b7280;margin:0;max-width:580px}
    .calc-card-form{background:#fff;border:1px solid #e5e7eb;border-radius:16px;padding:32px;margin-bottom:24px;box-shadow:0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,.06)}
    .calc-card-form h2{font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:700;color:#111827;margin:0 0 20px}
    .form-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:16px}
    @media(max-width:580px){.form-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
    .form-field{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:5px}
    .form-field.full{grid-column:1/-1}
    .form-field label{font-size:.82rem;font-weight:600;color:#374151}
    .input-wrap{position:relative;display:flex;align-items:center}
    .input-prefix{position:absolute;left:12px;font-size:.95rem;color:#9ca3af;pointer-events:none}
    .input-wrap input{padding-left:28px}
    .form-field input,.form-field select{border:1px solid #d1d5db;border-radius:8px;padding:9px 13px;font-size:.95rem;color:#111827;background:#f9fafb;transition:border-color .15s;width:100%;box-sizing:border-box}
    .form-field input:focus,.form-field select:focus{outline:none;border-color:#16a34a;background:#fff}
    .form-actions{margin-top:22px}
    .btn-calc{background:#16a34a;color:#fff;border:none;border-radius:10px;padding:12px 28px;font-size:1rem;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;transition:background .15s,transform .1s;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px}
    .btn-calc:hover{background:#15803d;transform:translateY(-1px)}
    .result-card{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f0fdf4 0%,#dcfce7 100%);border:1px solid #bbf7d0;border-radius:16px;padding:28px 32px;margin-bottom:24px}
    .result-card-header{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;margin-bottom:20px}
    .result-icon{width:38px;height:38px;background:#16a34a;border-radius:10px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center}
    .result-card-header h2{font-size:1rem;font-weight:700;color:#14532d;margin:0}
    .result-primary{background:#fff;border-radius:12px;padding:20px 24px;margin-bottom:16px}
    .result-primary .result-label{font-size:.85rem;font-weight:600;color:#6b7280;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.05em;display:block;margin-bottom:4px}
    .result-primary .result-amount{font-size:2.4rem;font-weight:800;color:#15803d}
    .result-primary .result-amount.owed{color:#dc2626}
    .result-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:12px}
    @media(max-width:520px){.result-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
    .result-item{background:#fff;border-radius:10px;padding:14px 16px}
    .result-item .ri-label{font-size:.78rem;color:#6b7280;font-weight:500;margin-bottom:3px}
    .result-item .ri-value{font-size:1.15rem;font-weight:700;color:#111827}
    .result-item .ri-value.green{color:#16a34a}.result-item .ri-value.red{color:#dc2626}
    .ad-zone{text-align:center;margin:28px 0;min-height:90px}
    .ad-zone-label{font-size:.7rem;color:#9ca3af;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.08em;margin-bottom:4px}
    .hiw-section{margin:48px 0 0}
    .section-eyebrow{font-size:.75rem;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.08em;color:#16a34a;margin-bottom:8px}
    .hiw-section h2,.faq-section h2,.related-section h2{font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:800;color:#111827;margin:0 0 8px}
    .hiw-section>p{color:#6b7280;margin:0 0 24px;font-size:.95rem}
    .hiw-steps{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:16px;margin-bottom:24px}
    .hiw-step{display:flex;gap:16px;align-items:flex-start;background:#fff;border:1px solid #e5e7eb;border-radius:12px;padding:18px 20px}
    .hiw-step-num{min-width:32px;height:32px;background:#f0fdf4;border:2px solid #bbf7d0;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:.85rem;font-weight:800;color:#16a34a}
    .hiw-step-body h3{font-size:.9rem;font-weight:700;color:#111827;margin:0 0 4px}
    .hiw-step-body p{font-size:.85rem;color:#6b7280;margin:0}
    .formula-box{background:#111827;border-radius:12px;padding:20px 24px;margin-bottom:24px;overflow-x:auto}
    .formula-box-label{font-size:.7rem;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.1em;color:#6b7280;margin-bottom:10px}
    .formula-box code{font-family:'Courier New',monospace;font-size:.85rem;color:#d1fae5;line-height:1.7;display:block;white-space:pre}
    .formula-box code .comment{color:#4b5563}.formula-box code .highlight{color:#34d399}
    .faq-section{margin:48px 0 0}
    .faq-section h2{margin-bottom:20px}
    .faq-list{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px}
    .faq-item{background:#fff;border:1px solid #e5e7eb;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden}
    .faq-question{width:100%;background:none;border:none;padding:17px 20px;text-align:left;font-size:.92rem;font-weight:600;color:#111827;cursor:pointer;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;gap:12px}
    .faq-question:hover{background:#f9fafb}
    .faq-chevron{min-width:20px;height:20px;border-radius:50%;background:#f3f4f6;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;transition:transform .2s}
    .faq-item.open .faq-chevron{transform:rotate(180deg);background:#dcfce7}
    .faq-answer{display:none;padding:0 20px 17px;font-size:.88rem;color:#6b7280;line-height:1.65}
    .faq-item.open .faq-answer{display:block}
    .related-section{margin:48px 0 0}
    .related-section h2{margin-bottom:16px}
    .related-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:14px}
    @media(max-width:580px){.related-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}}
    @media(max-width:380px){.related-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
    .related-card{background:#fff;border:1px solid #e5e7eb;border-radius:12px;padding:18px 16px;text-decoration:none;color:inherit;transition:border-color .15s,box-shadow .15s,transform .15s;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px}
    .related-card:hover{border-color:#16a34a;box-shadow:0 4px 12px rgba(22,163,74,.1);transform:translateY(-2px)}
    .related-card-icon{width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:9px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:2px}
    .related-card strong{font-size:.88rem;font-weight:700;color:#111827}
    .related-card span{font-size:.78rem;color:#9ca3af}
    .page-disclaimer{margin:40px 0 0;background:#f9fafb;border:1px solid #e5e7eb;border-radius:12px;padding:16px 20px;display:flex;gap:10px;align-items:flex-start}
    .page-disclaimer svg{color:#9ca3af;min-width:18px;margin-top:1px}
    .page-disclaimer p{font-size:.82rem;color:#6b7280;margin:0;line-height:1.55}
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header class="site-header">
    <nav class="nav">
      <a href="/" class="logo">
        <span class="logo-mark">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none">
            <rect x="1" y="1" width="8" height="8" rx="2" fill="#22c55e"/>
            <rect x="11" y="1" width="8" height="8" rx="2" fill="#22c55e" opacity="0.5"/>
            <rect x="1" y="11" width="8" height="8" rx="2" fill="#22c55e" opacity="0.5"/>
            <rect x="11" y="11" width="8" height="8" rx="2" fill="#22c55e" opacity="0.25"/>
          </svg>
        </span>
        <span>MyTaxCalcs</span>
      </a>
      <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/calculators">Calculators</a>
        <a href="/california-income-tax-calculator">States</a>
        <a href="/about">About</a>
        <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
      </div>
      <a class="nav-cta" href="/calculators">All Calculators</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
    <a href="/">Home</a>
    <span class="breadcrumb-sep">&#8250;</span>
    <a href="/calculators">Calculators</a>
    <span class="breadcrumb-sep">&#8250;</span>
    <span>Income Tax Calculator</span>
  </nav>

  <main>
    <div class="calc-page">

      <div class="calc-page-header">
        <div class="page-eyebrow">
          <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M7 8h4M7 12h8"/></svg>
          Federal Tax Estimator
        </div>
        <h1>Free Income Tax Calculator</h1>
        <p>Estimate your 2025 federal income tax, taxable income, refund or amount owed, effective tax rate, and marginal tax rate.</p>
      </div>

      <% if (result) { %>
      <div class="result-card">
        <div class="result-card-header">
          <div class="result-icon">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M7 8h4M7 12h8"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h2>Your Income Tax Estimate</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="result-primary">
          <span class="result-label"><%= result.refundOrOwed >= 0 ? 'Estimated Refund' : 'Estimated Amount Owed' %></span>
          <span class="result-amount <%= result.refundOrOwed >= 0 ? '' : 'owed' %>">$<%= Math.abs(Math.round(result.refundOrOwed)).toLocaleString() %></span>
        </div>
        <div class="result-grid">
          <div class="result-item">
            <div class="ri-label">Gross Income</div>
            <div class="ri-value">$<%= Math.round(result.grossIncome).toLocaleString() %></div>
          </div>
          <div class="result-item">
            <div class="ri-label">Deduction Used</div>
            <div class="ri-value">$<%= Math.round(result.deduction).toLocaleString() %></div>
          </div>
          <div class="result-item">
            <div class="ri-label">Taxable Income</div>
            <div class="ri-value">$<%= Math.round(result.taxableIncome).toLocaleString() %></div>
          </div>
          <div class="result-item">
            <div class="ri-label">Federal Tax After Credits</div>
            <div class="ri-value red">$<%= Math.round(result.federalTaxAfterCredits).toLocaleString() %></div>
          </div>
          <div class="result-item">
            <div class="ri-label">Effective Tax Rate</div>
            <div class="ri-value"><%= (result.effectiveTaxRate * 100).toFixed(1) %>%</div>
          </div>
          <div class="result-item">
            <div class="ri-label">Marginal Tax Rate</div>
            <div class="ri-value"><%= (result.marginalRate * 100).toFixed(1) %>%</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="ad-zone">
        <div class="ad-zone-label">Advertisement</div>
        <ins class="adsbygoogle" style="display:block"
          data-ad-client="ca-pub-5193834725888549"
          data-ad-slot="5205436277"
          data-ad-format="auto"
          data-full-width-responsive="true"></ins>
        <script>(adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});</script>
      </div>
      <% } %>

      <div class="calc-card-form">
        <h2>Enter Your Tax Information</h2>
        <form method="POST" action="/income-tax-calculator">
          <div class="form-grid">
            <div class="form-field full">
              <label for="grossIncome">Gross Annual Income</label>
              <div class="input-wrap">
                <span class="input-prefix">$</span>
                <input type="number" id="grossIncome" name="grossIncome" min="0" step="any"
                  value="<%= form.grossIncome || '' %>" placeholder="85000" required>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-field">
              <label for="filingStatus">Filing Status</label>
              <select id="filingStatus" name="filingStatus">
                <option value="single" <%= (!form.filingStatus || form.filingStatus === 'single') ? 'selected' : '' %>>Single</option>
                <option value="marriedJoint" <%= form.filingStatus === 'marriedJoint' ? 'selected' : '' %>>Married Filing Jointly</option>
                <option value="marriedSeparate" <%= form.filingStatus === 'marriedSeparate' ? 'selected' : '' %>>Married Filing Separately</option>
                <option value="headHousehold" <%= form.filingStatus === 'headHousehold' ? 'selected' : '' %>>Head of Household</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <div class="form-field">
              <label for="deductionType">Deduction Type</label>
              <select id="deductionType" name="deductionType">
                <option value="standard" <%= (!form.deductionType || form.deductionType === 'standard') ? 'selected' : '' %>>Standard Deduction</option>
                <option value="itemized" <%= form.deductionType === 'itemized' ? 'selected' : '' %>>Itemized Deduction</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <div class="form-field">
              <label for="itemizedDeduction">Itemized Deduction Amount</label>
              <div class="input-wrap">
                <span class="input-prefix">$</span>
                <input type="number" id="itemizedDeduction" name="itemizedDeduction" min="0" step="any"
                  value="<%= form.itemizedDeduction || '' %>" placeholder="0">
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-field">
              <label for="federalWithheld">Federal Tax Withheld</label>
              <div class="input-wrap">
                <span class="input-prefix">$</span>
                <input type="number" id="federalWithheld" name="federalWithheld" min="0" step="any"
                  value="<%= form.federalWithheld || '' %>" placeholder="12000">
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-field">
              <label for="taxCredits">Tax Credits</label>
              <div class="input-wrap">
                <span class="input-prefix">$</span>
                <input type="number" id="taxCredits" name="taxCredits" min="0" step="any"
                  value="<%= form.taxCredits || '' %>" placeholder="0">
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="form-actions">
            <button type="submit" class="btn-calc">
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M7 8h4M7 12h8"/></svg>
              Calculate Income Tax
            </button>
          </div>
        </form>
      </div>

      <div class="hiw-section">
        <div class="section-eyebrow">How It Works</div>
        <h2>How Federal Income Tax Is Calculated</h2>
        <p>The IRS uses a progressive bracket system. Here is how this calculator walks through each step.</p>
        <div class="hiw-steps">
          <div class="hiw-step">
            <div class="hiw-step-num">1</div>
            <div class="hiw-step-body">
              <h3>Start With Gross Income</h3>
              <p>Gross income includes wages, salaries, tips, self-employment income, and other taxable income before any deductions.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="hiw-step">
            <div class="hiw-step-num">2</div>
            <div class="hiw-step-body">
              <h3>Subtract Your Deduction</h3>
              <p>You can take the standard deduction for your filing status or itemize. Whichever is larger reduces your taxable income more.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="hiw-step">
            <div class="hiw-step-num">3</div>
            <div class="hiw-step-body">
              <h3>Apply Tax Brackets Progressively</h3>
              <p>Each bracket rate only applies to income within that bracket range, not your entire income. Lower brackets are always filled first.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="hiw-step">
            <div class="hiw-step-num">4</div>
            <div class="hiw-step-body">
              <h3>Subtract Credits and Withholding</h3>
              <p>Tax credits reduce your tax dollar for dollar. Subtracting withholding and credits from your tax liability gives the refund or balance owed.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="formula-box">
          <div class="formula-box-label">Formula Reference</div>
          <code><span class="comment">// Step 1 - Taxable Income</span>
<span class="highlight">Taxable Income</span>   = Gross Income - Deduction

<span class="comment">// Step 2 - 2025 Federal Brackets (Single filer)</span>
10%  on income up to $11,925
12%  on $11,925 to $48,475
22%  on $48,475 to $103,350
24%  on $103,350 to $197,300
32%  on $197,300 to $250,525
35%  on $250,525 to $626,350
37%  above $626,350

<span class="comment">// Step 3 - Refund or Owed</span>
<span class="highlight">Balance</span>          = (Tax - Credits) - Federal Withheld</code>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="ad-zone">
        <div class="ad-zone-label">Advertisement</div>
        <ins class="adsbygoogle" style="display:block"
          data-ad-client="ca-pub-5193834725888549"
          data-ad-slot="4212978293"
          data-ad-format="auto"
          data-full-width-responsive="true"></ins>
        <script>(adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});</script>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-section">
        <div class="section-eyebrow">FAQ</div>
        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <div class="faq-list">
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">Is this income tax calculator exact?<span class="faq-chevron"><svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg></span></button>
            <div class="faq-answer">No. This calculator provides an estimate only. Your actual result may differ based on credits, deductions, dependents, retirement contributions, business income, state taxes, and other tax rules.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">What is taxable income?<span class="faq-chevron"><svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg></span></button>
            <div class="faq-answer">Taxable income is the portion of your gross income remaining after subtracting deductions. The IRS applies tax brackets to this amount, not your full gross income.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">What is the difference between marginal and effective tax rate?<span class="faq-chevron"><svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg></span></button>
            <div class="faq-answer">Your marginal rate is the rate applied to the last dollar of your taxable income. Your effective rate is total estimated tax divided by gross income. Most people's effective rate is meaningfully lower than their marginal rate.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">Should I take the standard or itemized deduction?<span class="faq-chevron"><svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg></span></button>
            <div class="faq-answer">Take whichever is larger. Common itemized deductions include mortgage interest, state and local taxes (up to $10,000), and charitable contributions. The 2025 standard deduction is $15,000 for single filers and $30,000 for married filing jointly.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">Does this calculator include state income tax?<span class="faq-chevron"><svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg></span></button>
            <div class="faq-answer">No, this page estimates federal income tax only. Use the state calculator pages linked below for state-specific estimates.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">What tax year does this calculator use?<span class="faq-chevron"><svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg></span></button>
            <div class="faq-answer">This calculator uses 2025 federal tax brackets and standard deduction amounts. Tax brackets are adjusted annually for inflation by the IRS.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="related-section">
        <h2>Related Tax Calculators</h2>
        <div class="related-grid">
          <a class="related-card" href="/tax-refund-calculator">
            <div class="related-card-icon" style="background:#f0fdf4;color:#15803d;"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="23"/><path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 000 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 010 7H6"/></svg></div>
            <strong>Tax Refund Calculator</strong>
            <span>Estimate your federal refund or balance owed</span>
